Description:
  Scaffolds a new Kiso component with all required files:
  theme module, ERB partial, Lookbook preview, and docs page.

  This generator is for internal Kiso development only.

Examples:
  # Basic component
  bin/rails generate kiso:component tooltip

  # Colored component with two-axis color x variant compound variants
  bin/rails generate kiso:component notification --colored

  # Component with sub-parts
  bin/rails generate kiso:component card --sub-parts header content footer

  # Component with Stimulus controller
  bin/rails generate kiso:component accordion --stimulus

  # All options combined
  bin/rails generate kiso:component alert --colored --sub-parts title description close --stimulus

  # Skip docs page
  bin/rails generate kiso:component tooltip --skip-docs

Generated files:
  lib/kiso/themes/{name}.rb                                    Theme module
  app/views/kiso/components/_{name}.html.erb                   ERB partial
  app/views/kiso/components/{name}/_{part}.html.erb            Sub-part partials (with --sub-parts)
  test/components/previews/kiso/{name}_preview.rb              Lookbook preview class
  test/components/previews/kiso/{name}_preview/playground.html.erb  Preview template
  app/javascript/controllers/kiso/{name}_controller.js         Stimulus controller (with --stimulus)
  docs/src/components/{name}.md                                Docs page (unless --skip-docs)
